item.title: Release Notes
item.description: sectionStart v.1.0.15 # Add ConcreteTypeDefinition in ArbitraryProperty, deprecate getChildPropertiesByResolvedProperty and getChildPropertyListsByCandidateProperty which is added in 1.0.14. sectionEnd sectionStart v.1.0.14 # Add supporting value class with the private constructor. Add supporting for sealed class and sealed interface. Deprecate nullInject and childPropertyListsByCandidateProperty properties in ObjectNode. They would be moved to ArbitraryProperty. sectionEnd sectionStart v.1.0.13 # Add InterfacePlugin supports abstract classes through abstractClassExtends option. Fix setLazy with value wrapped by Just would not be manipulated.
